{{Quote|Uh, Chief Chirpa, do these come any bigger?|Wicket W. Warrick|<ref name="Night of the Stranger">{{Ewoks|Night of the Stranger}}</ref>}}
'''Beads of Bravery''' were ceremonial beads presented to [[Ewok/Legends|Ewoks]] of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]] as an award for bravery in dangerous conflicts. The Ewok children, [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket Wystri Warrick]], [[Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka/Legends|Kneesaa a Jari Kintaka]], [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]], and [[Latara/Legends|Latara]] were all awarded Beads of Bravery for their service in the [[Stranger War]]. Wicket thereafter wore the bead as a trophy on his new [[Belt of Honor]] to replace the one which had been lost during the defeat of the [[Stranger]].

